title: $:/changenotes/5.5.0/#9740
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

* Bare URLs in wikitext now include closing parentheses when they balance an opening one inside the URL, so `https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Specials_(Unicode_block)` links completely; a URL wrapped in prose parentheses like `(see https://example.com/)` still excludes the wrapping `)` (fixes [[Issue #9298|https://github.com/TiddlyWiki/TiddlyWiki5/issues/9298]])
